author: ETA PRIME
description:
We’re taking a first look at the all-new KONKR Pocket Fit—AYANEO’s new sub-brand aimed at lower prices. In this video we unbox the Pocket Fit, cover the full specs, and run early gameplay and emulation tests. Configs include a Snapdragon G3 series chipset or the Pocket Fit Elite with Snapdragon 8 Elite, a sharp 6" 144Hz display, and up to 16GB RAM. Watch for our impressions on performance, controls, and overall value.

Learn More Here: https://www.indiegogo.com/projects/pocket-fit-premier-hi-performance-android-handheld#/
